title: Huge 2br plus den in NE Minneapolis
posting_body: ['Available between august 25th and September 1, 2022', 'Huge 2 bedroom plus den...', 'Youtube Video of Apartment <URL>', 'This renovated smoker free apartment is a few blocks from breweries, resultants and coffee shops.', 'Everything is clean and in good working order.', 'There are security lights and cameras on each side of building.', 'The home is monitored, maintained and occupied by the owner.', 'Utilities - Renter pays gas and electric.', 'Property Care Yard / Snow duties-', 'Rotate monthly between the two apartments.', 'Parking-', 'One off street parking space is included.', 'Laundry- Laundry is shared coin in basement.', 'Pets- Cats are ok and are $20/month.', 'There is no pet deposit.', 'Dogs are not allowed.', 'Landlord pays for water and trash.', 'There is also a reliable and fast internet signal that renters can use at no charge.', 'Smoking - Not allowed anywhere on the property.', 'Screening - Screening in weighted order and within reg constraints 1) Criminal background cannot include any feloniez. 2) No history eviction or unlawful detainer.', '3) Good Credit 4) 2yr good rental history 5) subject to income requirement.', '1yr min term Non-smokers only.', 'No co-signors.', 'To be really clear-', 'This is a quiet building and there is no smoking allowed anywhere inside the building or outside the building - no smoking']
